data.description: 20 minutes from Galveston TX and 25 mins from Webster TX the home of the newest Great Wolf Lodge opening 2024.   Wouldn't you love being in the center of it all? You will have the privacy of a gated community,  with a neighboring Yacht Club, community swimming pool and miniature golf! This home features 3 bedrooms 2.5 baths, an elevator and a sauna! There are 2 fireplaces - one of which is located in the Primary Bedroom along with a private balcony overlooking the bay. The Primary Bedroom boasts views of the bay as ships and barges move into and out of the Galveston Area. The main wrap around porch has an outdoor kitchen located off the dining area. The Dining area is next to the kitchen that displays high end stainless steel appliances.  This beauty sits on a double lot which also means you will have access to 2 boat slips. The price is inclusive of the furniture and tankless water heater. BRING YOUR PREAPPROVAL LETTERS/POFs AND SNAG THIS ONE AND EXTEND YOUR SUMMER!
